# No Microsoft intellectual property in git.
# The Graph OpenAPI spec, any derived subset, and ogen-generated code (a derivative
# of the spec) are fetched + generated at BUILD time, never checked in. These
# patterns guard against accidental commits wherever the build places them.
openapi-full.yaml
openapi-subset.yaml

# ogen-generated package (derivative of the spec) — regenerated by `go generate`.
# The canonical `go generate ./internal/graph` writes the first path; `/api/`
# is a safety net for a stray `go run ./cmd/gen-graph-api` from the repo root.
/internal/graph/api/
/api/

# mailboxd binary from `go build ./cmd/mailboxd`
/mailboxd
